  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Open label study to evaluate the efficacy of CURE-EX device in the treatment of
      onychomycosis.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Each affected nail will be treated twice daily for 24-30 weeks. Efficacy will be evaluated by
      measuring the growth of healthy nail.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
